@startuml
title AI Study Buddy - Focus State Machine

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFCFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #2E8B57
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam roundCorner 12
skinparam state {
  BorderColor #4BA36B
  FontColor #173B26
  BackgroundColor #E6F7EA
}

[*] --> Idle
state Idle #EAF2FF

Idle --> Calibrating : Start session
state Calibrating #FFF7DB
Calibrating --> Tracking : Calibration complete

state Tracking #E6F7EA {
  [*] --> Focused

  state Focused #D7F2E1
  state Distracted #FFE7D6
  state Uncertain #FFF7DB

  Focused : Primary label = screen
  Distracted : Primary label = away_*
  Uncertain : Confidence below threshold

  Focused --> Distracted : Away persists > 2.5s
  Distracted --> Focused : Screen persists > 1.0s

  Focused --> Uncertain : confidence < 0.55
  Distracted --> Uncertain : confidence < 0.55
  Uncertain --> Focused : stable focused signal
  Uncertain --> Distracted : stable distracted signal
}

Tracking --> Ended : Stop session
state Ended #EAF2FF
Ended --> [*]

note right of Tracking
Temporal guardrails:
- EMA smoothing alpha = 0.35
- Min dwell between transitions = 0.5s
- Hysteresis avoids rapid label flapping
end note

@enduml
